NoShadows (Material global keyword)
===================================

Description
-----------

Prevents this material from casting shadows onto any surfaces.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

`noShadows`

Parameters
----------

Not Available.

Notes
-----

This implies the [NoSelfShadow](NoSelfShadow\_(Material\_global\_keyword)) global keyword.


